Description:
O reuso de objetos e a ressignificação é uma tendência no mercado;

Compra e venda de mercadorias, itens antigos, novos colecionáveis, raridades. 

Compra de objetos para colocação em leilões online.

@friendsofleon

Friends of Léon erbjuder noga utvald och kvalitets second hand kläder och leksaker för barn. 
Hos oss kan ni hitta både pre-loved av finaste kvalité och fynda bland oanvända varor som vi tagit in via samarbeten från bland annat tidigare kollektioner eller utgående modeller. Vi strävar efter att allt ska komma till användning.

Hunan Xinyuan Recycling Technology Co., Ltd. was established in 2022(registered capital: 50 million RMB), our E-commerce Department specializes in cost-effective IT infrastructure equipment and components for enterprise clients. Core offerings include:
Networking: Enterprise-grade switches, high-speed modules;
Computing Hardware: Refurbished servers (e.g., Dell/HP series), workstations;
Storage Solutions: Server HDDs/SSDs (1TB-16TB), RAM (DDR3/DDR4/DDR5), RAID controllers;
Customization: Hardware upgrades and bulk procurement plans.
With rigorous refurbishment processes (72-hour stress testing, deep cleaning) and ISO 9001 certification, we deliver near-new performance and 1-3 years tiered warranties. Compliant with CE/RoHS standards, our products meet global data center requirements. Via Alibaba International, we provide efficient logistics (DDP/DAP), multilingual support, and flexible terms (OEM/ODM) to reduce IT costs and promote sustainable IT ecosystems.
